auto_abilities_data.name: sensor
auto_abilities_data.game_description: View enemy data during battle.
auto_abilities_data.description: Shows enemy HP, elemental resistances, active statuses, and a brief description, while the user is in the active party.

auto_abilities_data.name: piercing
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Deal normal damage to armored enemies.
auto_abilities_data.description: Attacks and skills ignore enemy's Armoured status.

auto_abilities_data.name: first strike
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Act first at beginning of battle.
auto_abilities_data.description: Guarantees the first turn during battle even in an ambush.

auto_abilities_data.name: initiative
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Raises party's chances for a preemptive strike.
auto_abilities_data.description: Raises party's chances for a preemptive strike and eliminates ambushes, except against enemys with a 100% ambush rate.

auto_abilities_data.name: firestrike
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Adds fire element to attacks and skills.
auto_abilities_data.description: Causes the user's Attacks and Skills to be fire-elemental.

auto_abilities_data.name: lightningstrike
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Adds lightning element to attacks and skills.
auto_abilities_data.description: Causes the user's Attacks and Skills to be lightning-elemental.

auto_abilities_data.name: darktouch
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Sometimes adds darkness to attacks and skills.
auto_abilities_data.description: Causes the user's Attacks and Skills to have a 50% base chance to inflict darkness for three turns. Chance stacks additively with darkstrike.

auto_abilities_data.name: darkstrike
auto_abilities_data.game_description: Almost always adds darkness to attacks and skills.
auto_abilities_data.description: Causes the user's Attacks and Skills to have a 100% base chance to inflict darkness for three turns. Chance stacks additively with darktouch.
